sequenceDiagram
    participant VLLMPod as vLLM/SGLang Pod<br/>5557/TCP ZMQ PUB
    participant ZMQSub as ZMQ Subscriber<br/>5557/TCP ZMQ SUB
    participant Pool as kvevents.Pool<br/>Sharded Workers
    participant Adapter as Engine Adapter<br/>(vLLM/SGLang)
    participant Index as kvblock.Index<br/>(InMemory/Redis)
    participant EPP as llm-d EPP<br/>(Host Scheduler)
    participant Indexer as KV-Cache Indexer<br/>ScoreTokens API
    participant TokenProc as TokenProcessor<br/>FNV-64a
    participant UdsClient as UDS Tokenizer Client<br/>gRPC over UDS
    participant UdsServer as UDS Tokenizer Server<br/>Python gRPC Sidecar
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant FSBackend as llmd_fs_backend<br/>Python/C++/CUDA
    participant Storage as Shared Storage<br/>(NFS/PVC)

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over VLLMPod,Index: Flow 1: KV-Event Ingestion (Write Path)
        VLLMPod->>ZMQSub: ZMQ PUB (msgpack)<br/>5557/TCP, No encryption
        ZMQSub->>Pool: Go channel (in-process)
        Note right of Pool: FNV-1a hash of pod ID<br/>→ deterministic worker
        Pool->>Adapter: Dispatch to worker<br/>msgpack decode
        Adapter->>Index: Add(engineKey, requestKey, pod)<br/>or Evict(engineKey)
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over EPP,TokenProc: Flow 2: Pod Scoring (Read Path)
        EPP->>Indexer: ScoreTokens(tokens, model, pods)<br/>Go API (in-process)
        Indexer->>TokenProc: ComputeBlockKeys(tokens)<br/>FNV-64a hash chunks
        TokenProc-->>Indexer: []BlockKey
        Indexer->>Index: Lookup(blockKeys)
        Index-->>Indexer: map[pod]matchedBlocks
        Indexer->>Indexer: Score(matches, totalBlocks)
        Indexer-->>EPP: map[string]float64<br/>(pod → cache-hit score)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over EPP,UdsServer: Flow 3: Tokenization (Sidecar)
        EPP->>UdsClient: Tokenize(prompt, model)
        UdsClient->>UdsServer: gRPC over UDS<br/>/tmp/tokenizer/tokenizer-uds.socket<br/>No encryption (local IPC)
        Note right of UdsServer: vLLM OpenAIServingRender<br/>(CPU mode)
        UdsServer-->>UdsClient: TokenIDs[]
        UdsClient-->>EPP: TokenIDs[]

        Note over UdsServer,HFHub: First-time tokenizer init
        UdsServer->>HFHub: Download tokenizer<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP, TLS 1.2+
        HFHub-->>UdsServer: Tokenizer model files
    end

    rect rgb(255, 230, 230)
        Note over VLLMPod,Storage: Flow 4: KV-Cache Offloading (fs_backend)
        VLLMPod->>FSBackend: OffloadingConnector API<br/>(Python/C++ in-process)
        FSBackend->>Storage: POSIX write<br/>GPU → Host → Disk
        Note right of FSBackend: C++/CUDA handles<br/>GPU-to-host copies
        Storage-->>FSBackend: ACK
        FSBackend-->>VLLMPod: Offload complete

        Note over VLLMPod,Storage: KV-Cache Restore
        VLLMPod->>FSBackend: Restore request
        FSBackend->>Storage: POSIX read
        Storage-->>FSBackend: KV-cache blocks
        FSBackend-->>VLLMPod: Blocks loaded to GPU
    end
